          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Lori Jackson Domestic Violence Survivor Protection Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to modify the prohibition on firearm sale or transfer to or purchase or possession by an individual who is subject to a court order that restrains the individual from harassing, stalking, or threatening an intimate partner or child of an intimate partner. Specifically, the bill revises the elements of a qualifying court order. It also broadens the definition of &quot;intimate partner&quot; to include a dating partner or former dating partner.</p>]]></text>
